highlights.text: “Without You” by 高爾宣 OSN has been on Top Songs Taiwan the longest, at 2327 days straight.

“瑪格莉塔 Margarita” by 莫宰羊, Tyson Yoshi, Patrick Brasca, 婁峻碩, and Juice Boy is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Taiwan, up 87 spots at #74.
